    %section 
        %h2.s4 Convincing SSB to take the leap
        %p.no-image I created two other prototypes to refine the idea and get buy-in from SSB leadership. With the help of the prototypes and research findings, the Tuft & Needle management team was able to convince the SSB leadership team to move forward with this idea of configurable products.

    %section.summary
        %p.large This project laid the groundwork for the successful relaunch of custom e-commerce sites for both Beautyrest and Serta and is on track to change the way both brands handle product strategy moving forward.

